{"tid":2264920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"呂智恆涉阻清牆 指查問身份不獲回應  便衣食環拒騷證稱怯場","createTime":"2020-10-31T04:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T06:15:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fd395763e78002fd7dee40c1f58dcf6eba3a2f56","tid":2264920,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T04:47:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/3CXICPY7PNFGLH7B4PLL5R7JT4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2F3CXICPY7PNFGLH7B4PLL5R7JT4%2F&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdj4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=b4f8e9b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2F3CXICPY7PNFGLH7B4PLL5R7JT4%2F&h=ead18c57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/3CXICPY7PNFGLH7B4PLL5R7JT4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n呂智恆涉阻清牆 指查問身份不獲回應 <br />\n便衣食環拒騷證稱怯場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6DOEd0HoqSCo-Fv1M4uVCgUur1w=/1328x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LTGBTLSCPFHGXOVJKEDXN24CEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6DOEd0HoqSCo-Fv1M4uVCgUur1w%3D%2F1328x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLTGBTLSCPFHGXOVJKEDXN24CEU.jpg&h=df929e8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■麥慶安昨在庭上承認無出示證件。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】社工呂智恆被指阻礙食環署職員清理「連儂牆」文宣，遭控以阻礙公職人員罪，案件昨日開審。現場影片顯示涉案食環署一級督察當時身穿便服，被告則一度稱他為「外判商職員」。涉案督察作供時坦言，當時沒穿制服或出示委任證，僅口頭表明身份，被告或聽不清楚，根本不知他是食環署職員。督察又解釋，當時被告正在拍片，他擔心會被即場公開個人資料，故沒有出示委任證，「我認係有怯場」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：官轟控方屢錯「四單都係咁」<br />\n<br />\n被告呂智恆（38歲）被控於。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n麥慶安昨供稱，當日他帶同路政署人員及外判清潔工，打算到上址清理違例文宣，其間被告用揚聲器詢問行動詳情。為免拖延行動，麥要求警方支援。其後麥和外判清潔工等人在警方陪同下重返天橋，但被告仍站在連儂牆前阻礙。被告被捕後，麥等人終成功清理牆上文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qbttzCtZ-pzbhTzrQUgUgWxg-2k=/1202x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WFSCC3ZZZNERXLDHRFRQBDFZHE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqbttzCtZ-pzbhTzrQUgUgWxg-2k%3D%2F1202x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWFSCC3ZZZNERXLDHRFRQBDFZHE.jpg&h=c070d05e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■食環署一級督察麥慶安案發當日無穿制服，被告呂智恆持咪與他對質。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/n_GeAmvqLWPdtkXsTps9m4Vhvp0=/2128x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LOTGBXRA3FHFXHTYGVM2O5TITM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fn_GeAmvqLWPdtkXsTps9m4Vhvp0%3D%2F2128x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLOTGBXRA3FHFXHTYGVM2O5TITM.jpg&h=da6513f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■呂智恆被控阻礙公職人員罪，昨到庭應訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警稱被告「消極嘅阻礙」<br />\n<br />\n惟裁判官陳炳宙觀看事發片段後揚言，「我開到好大聲，耳仔貼住咁滯」，但由始至終只聽到麥自稱「姓麥」，沒透露食環署職員身份。麥強調當時確有表明職員身份，惟影片未必拍攝到。<br />\n<br />\n陳官又質疑，為何被告問麥是否「外判商職員」時，麥沒有重申身份。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指出，影片顯示被告查問行動細節、法律基礎及麥的職業時，麥回應稱：。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n拘捕被告的警署警長黎文毅（譯音）在辯方盤問下，同意被告在現場從沒說出侮辱性言詞，情緒亦不激動。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳官裁定案件表證成立。辯方不傳召證人作供。案件下月24日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：FLS2398/20"},{"pid":"e2519178cf460ba95086609b999a4cd495425148","tid":2264920,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T04:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f2c6708e6ef86fc07d6b11d992861b5d16923e","tid":2264920,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T04:50:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"54a619debf35f605f691ec414e1